    CharClass, Group

    public abstract class AbstractQuantifiableSequenceableAlternative
extends AbstractSequenceableAlternative
implements Quantifiable
    Extension to AbstractSequenceableAlternative providing the canonical implementation of Quantifiable. Note that it delegates to static methods of Quantified.
